%^BOLD%^CYAN%^ULINE%^Arcane Bloodline%^RESET%^

Your family has always been skilled in the eldritch art of magic. While many of your relatives were accomplished wizards, your powers developed without the need for study and practice.

%^CYAN%^BOLD%^Bloodline Arcana:%^RESET%^
You are particularly adept at the use of metamagic. When applying metamagic to a spell, increase that spell's DC by 1.

%^CYAN%^BOLD%^Arcane Bond (L31):%^RESET%^
You gain use of the arcane bond feat, and can summon a familiar. The Sorcerer also gains one additional bonus mastery slot (like spell knowledge).

%^CYAN%^BOLD%^Bonus Bloodline Skill%^RESET%^: none

%^CYAN%^BOLD%^Bonus Spells%^RESET%^: identify, invisibility, dispel magic, dimension door, siphon magic, true seeing, limited wish, powerword stun, disjunction
